divs: Sighting DetailsI was at home just sitting around with my fiance and his friend, We were looking up at the stars and I noticed the first object, then two more objects appearred, when the first object appeared I though that it was an airplane but when the other two objects appeared and they werent moving I thought to myself that they could nt be airplanes because they have no noise and I live not to far from Whiteman airforce base and have jets and helicopters come over my house all the time and this was neither. The objects were sphere shaped and seemed to be hovering in the same spots with three lighs going in opposite directions Red, White and Blue. I was fascinated couldnt take my eyes away I tried to capture the image with my phone but it wouldnt show up as it was to high. It just kinda fizzled out.
Summary: 3 objects in different directions with pulsating lights
